metadata.name: Immersed in Nature
metadata.description: The other day Nature kindly invited me to meet her. She asked me to come a little closer, to listen to her, to feel her, to touch her. As soon as I did, something happened, little by little she enveloped my mind and transported me to a universe where I only experienced freedom. I have another date with her today.
